---
title: Black Rice, Mushroom & Miso Kale Salad with Pickled Cucumber, Sweet Potato & Sesame Dressing
description: Step aside, side salad—this hearty kale version is the stuff of dinner dreams. We toss the tender greens with miso black rice, roasted mushrooms and sweet potato, tangy pickled cucumbers, and a nutty sesame dressing. This healthy, hearty-yet-light-feeling dinner is one you’re going to want to make again and again.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/miso-shroom-sweet-potato-kale-salad-9c42accd.jpg
